snippet.title: Project 007 - Nintendo Switch 2 Trailer | Nintendo Switch 2 Direct
snippet.description:
IO Interactive the developers of Hitman are making a 007 James Bond game and it's coming to Nintendo Switch 2. Don't miss this Project 007 trailer.

#007 #JamesBond #Nintendo
